title: [Solhaven, Kraken and Tentacle]
[Solhaven, Kraken Run]
description: Plank tables line the sides of both streets near the intersection, interspersed with barrels and bushel baskets, all of them laden with fruits and vegetables and attended by vendors claiming the greatest freshness and lowest prices.  Locally grown produce is easily distinguishable from what has arrived by ship or overland, but the variety is impressive.
